The String Template I still remember when writing print statements in Java, I managed to make the output look more readable by appending text with the variable. Something like this
System.out.println(arr[i] + &quot; &quot; + &quot;From for loop&quot;);
Now this will change from Java 21 as String Template is here. Example program demonstrating String Template What is String Template? String Template is a process of substituting values of variables into placeholders in a string.
